PC-ABS Alloy Resin Market FAQs
1. What is PC-ABS alloy resin?
PC-ABS alloy resin is a blend of polycarbonate and acrylonitrile-butadiene-styrene (ABS) plastics, known for their high impact resistance and heat resistance.

2. What are the key applications of PC-ABS alloy resin?
PC-ABS alloy resin is commonly used in automotive parts, electronics, appliances, and industrial equipment due to its strength and heat resistance.

